        "about": "Berkarir di {location} menawarkan berbagai peluang menarik karena kota ini merupakan pusat ekonomi, bisnis, dan industri terbesar di Indonesia. Dengan banyaknya perusahaan multinasional, startup, dan industri kreatif, Jakarta menyediakan ruang bagi berbagai profesi dan latar belakang karir. Selain gaji yang kompetitif, kota ini juga menawarkan akses ke jaringan profesional yang luas, serta peluang untuk berkembang dan belajar dari para pemimpin industri.",
        "about_en": "in {location} every day exclusively on Dealls. Building a career in {location} offers various exciting opportunities, as the city is the largest economic, business, and industrial hub in Indonesia. With numerous multinational companies, startups, and creative industries, {location} provides space for professionals from various fields and career backgrounds. In addition to competitive salaries, the city also offers access to a wide professional network, as well as opportunities to grow and learn from industry leaders.",
